prose.content:
Used on a party Pokémon
:   Cures [sleep](https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Sleep_(status_condition)){mechanic}.

This Pokémon's damaging moves have a 10% chance to make the target [flinch](https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Flinch_(status_condition)){mechanic} with each hit if they do not already cause flinching as a secondary effect.

This ability does not stack with a held item.

Overworld: The wild encounter rate is halved while this Pokémon is first in the party.

damageClass.name: Physical
damageClass.description: Physical damage, controlled by Attack and Defense

description.content: One other Pokémon on the field, selected by the trainer.

long.content: Inflicts regular damage.  Ignores [accuracy](https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Accuracy){mechanic} and [evasion](https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Stat#Evasion){mechanic} modifiers.
